data.title: Fund Utilization Report 2016 17 CompressPdf
data.meta_description: Fund Utilization Report 2016 17 CompressPdf - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides a fund utilization report from the Office of the Dean, Alumni & Corporate Relations at Indian Institute of Technology Bombay for the 2016-2017 financial year. It outlines how donations from alumni and corporations were utilized to support student development, faculty development, infrastructure projects, class projects, endowments, lecture series, and major events organized by the Dean's office. Donations supported scholarships, fellowships, awards, new research centers and laboratories, professorships, and various academic and alumni engagement initiatives. The report demonstrates how alumni and corporate donations were invested across different areas to further the institute's pursuit of excellence in education and research.
